    := compSL C(spectrum ‚Ąā a, ‚Ąā) _ _ _ _ (toLinearFunctional x y) (cfcCLM ha)
```

This defines `cfc_toLinearFunctional x y f` as `‚ü™x, (cfcCLM ha f) y‚üę_‚Ąā`.

