```

Next property: `P ‚Č• 0`.

```tactics
    constructor
    ¬∑ -- Show that the map is positive
      intro x
      simp [continuousLinearMapOfBilin, toBoundedBilin, toLinearFunctional, cfc_toLinearFunctional, cfcCLM, cfcHom]
      positivity
```

Last property: `P` is idempotent.

```tactics
    ¬∑ -- Show that the map is idempotent
      simp [continuousLinearMapOfBilin, toBoundedBilin, toLinearFunctional, cfc_toLinearFunctional, cfcCLM, cfcHom]
```

This completes the proof of `isOrthogonalProjection'`.

